The Second Spanish Republic is yet another false idol that will ultimately fail to save mankind from exploitation and oppression. We should keep cool while the people are celebrating and while we express our own enthusiasm at the King's flight, we can also forewarn that the Republic's reign doesn't mean the beginning of social harmony, as even some members of the CNT naively believe. 

